title: Bridget Moynahan got married! Blue Bloods actress shares photo from the wedding!
text:
Tweet 
Bridget Moynahan married businessman Andrew Frankel yesterday in a ceremony that took place in the Hamptons. 
The Blue Bloods star, 44, shared a picture from her big day looking stunning and very happy next to her partner in a garden. 
“Oh, by the way, guess what I just did @johndolanphotog #sohappy #perfection #friends #family #forever,” she wrote on her Instagram page. A photo posted by Bridget Moynahan (@bridgetmoynahan) on Oct 17, 2015 at 5:36pm PDT 
According to a source cited by People magazine, the bride and groom “met each other through a friend and she has been on cloud nine ever since.” 
Previously, Moynahan dated New England Patriots quarterback Tom Brady, 38, from 2004 to 2006, with whom she has eight-year-old son Jack. Spread the rumor
